brian
said...
<div class='commentnumber' style='font-size: 20px;padding:0 10px;'>
<a href='#comment-1688229466183814475' id='comment-1688229466183814475' style='float:right; margin-top:-20px;' title='Comment permalink'>
<script type='text/javascript'>
CommentsCounter=CommentsCounter+1; document.write(CommentsCounter)
