ting some strange hits and my intuition in my own experience is more accurate than any other quality I possess.<br /><br />So I&#39;m looking to get as much input as possible which is part of the reason why I laid it out as I did. I&#39;m just going to have to ask you to trust me for a little while. I believe I have earned that/</p>
