<p>aDeception Airborne flying into yonder eyes<br />playing hob&#39;d abogado with bits of twist tried<br />count alfred and sarlo outside, homburgs with fries<br />kneeslapping milo too hard so he flies...<br /><br />odd belief-ablity some sell that is not even owned<br />to ones who come looking at clean dusted bones<br />geometric&#39;ly spread now a virus through phones<br />that maybe a little there sounds like pheromones...<br /><br />it seems we&#39;ll wind up in similar straits, in valles, on peaks<br />scattering winds as sheaths open in wee timid streaks<br />a tad scraping off wiped into air fitfully filled as light leaks<br />into there. i think titles give oomph and so &quot;Silliness Shrieks&quot;...<br /><br />there&#39;s only a few words paltry and lame<br />a dogfight, response or reply no need to acclaim<br />accompany your voice, mine - i listen all day<br />let&#39;s hear what your nimble&#39;d fingers can play...<br /><br />miphi</p>
